when your friends
are there, right?

282
00:12:26,200 --> 00:12:27,767
What's happening?

283
00:12:29,733 --> 00:12:32,000
Oh, okay.

284
00:12:32,133 --> 00:12:33,433
You're fooling them.

285
00:12:33,567 --> 00:12:35,633
Oh my, don't believe him.

286
00:12:35,767 --> 00:12:37,467
He has no girlfriend.

287
00:12:39,433 --> 00:12:40,833
You, Selena,

288
00:12:40,967 --> 00:12:43,100
