289
00:12:43,233 --> 00:12:46,667
Well, I'm just training
these guys,

290
00:12:46,800 --> 00:12:50,033
so I need to impress them
so they can learn.

291
00:12:50,200 --> 00:12:53,200
You don't need to lie
to impress them.

292
00:12:53,733 --> 00:12:55,700
There are so many things that
they can like about you.

293
00:13:07,900 --> 00:13:09,767
Oh, there, these are real
flowers.

294
00:13:10,800 --> 00:13:13,267
I guess this will pass
with Bobby.

295
00:13:14,700 --> 00:13:15,867
There's Tonyo, oh!

296
00:13:17,333 --> 00:13:19,167
- Sir Tonyo!
- Oh?

297
00:13:19,300 --> 00:13:20,500
Sir Tonyo, help us!

298
00:13:20,633 --> 00:13:22,033
Oh, what happened?

299
00:13:22,200 --> 00:13:23,133
Oh, it's just an emergency.

300
00:13:23,267 --> 00:13:24,800
We need you.

301
00:13:24,933 --> 00:13:26,767
Oh my, I'm going to Bobby.

302
00:13:26,900 --> 00:13:28,200
What emergency is that?

303
00:13:28,333 --> 00:13:29,633
Sir Tonyo, it's just
a quick one.

304
00:13:29,767 --> 00:13:31,300
You're the only one
who can help us.

305
00:13:31,433 --> 00:13:32,167
- Let's go!
- Let's go! This will be quick.

306
00:13:32,300 --> 00:13:33,700
It will take only a moment,
okay?

307
00:13:33,833 --> 00:13:34,733
Where is that?

308
00:13:34,867 --> 00:13:35,600
Here.

309
00:13:36,867 --> 00:13:38,700
Well, Ma'am Bobby and Sir Tonyo,

310
00:13:38,833 --> 00:13:41,367
