to reconcile them?

311
00:13:41,500 --> 00:13:43,467
Hey...

312
00:13:43,600 --> 00:13:45,167
Change topic.

313
00:13:46,567 --> 00:13:48,433
Bok, oh...

314
00:13:48,567 --> 00:13:50,133
those two, oh...

315
00:13:50,267 --> 00:13:51,633
it's hopeless.

316
00:13:51,767 --> 00:13:53,000
You're too much.

317
00:13:53,133 --> 00:13:54,233
They're not even a couple yet,

318
00:13:54,400 --> 00:13:56,133
