329
00:14:13,100 --> 00:14:15,133
Can we date them?

330
00:14:16,733 --> 00:14:18,033
Yes, those guys are single,

331
00:14:18,167 --> 00:14:20,800
but I'm 100 percent sure,

332
00:14:20,933 --> 00:14:22,333
