333
00:14:23,600 --> 00:14:24,900
Okay, I'm leaving.

334
00:14:25,033 --> 00:14:26,667
That's all.

335
00:14:26,800 --> 00:14:28,667
And you, next time, tell me

336
00:14:28,833 --> 00:14:30,500
if you want to impress them.

337
00:14:30,633 --> 00:14:31,567
I can handle that.

338
00:14:31,700 --> 00:14:33,033
We can pretend that we bumped
into each other,

339
00:14:33,167 --> 00:14:34,400
then I stumble,

340
00:14:34,533 --> 00:14:36,200
then I slowly stand up,

341
00:14:36,333 --> 00:14:38,667
then we stare at each other,
like in slow-mo.

342
00:14:38,800 --> 00:14:42,267
Too bad, that would have been
like a movie.

343
00:14:44,867 --> 00:14:48,000
Sir, it seems you and Selena
look good together.

344
00:14:48,133 --> 00:14:50,500
Yes, you have the same
wavelength.

345
00:14:57,400 --> 00:14:58,967
Oh my.

346
00:15:04,500 --> 00:15:06,433
Unbelievable.

347
00:15:06,567 --> 00:15:09,167
Sir Tonyo!

348
00:15:18,433 --> 00:15:19,933
Oh...

349
00:15:21,300 --> 00:15:22,633
Why are you wearing that?

350
00:15:22,767 --> 00:15:24,867
Maybe someone will see you, huh?

351
00:15:25,000 --> 00:15:26,300
Oh, Sir Tonyo, don't worry.

352
00:15:26,433 --> 00:15:29,067
Our dorm mates
aren't here today.

353
00:15:30,767 --> 00:15:33,333
Do we look good in this,
Sir Tonyo?

354
00:15:33,467 --> 00:15:35,067
Oh...

355
00:15:35,233 --> 00:15:36,333
Oh...

356
00:15:36,467 --> 00:15:38,000
Wait a minute.

357
00:15:38,133 --> 00:15:40,400
Is this the emergency
you're talking about?

358
00:15:40,533 --> 00:15:42,167
Of course, Sir Tonyo.

359
00:15:42,300 --> 00:15:45,167
Fashion emergency
is still an emergency.

360
00:15:45,300 --> 00:15:46,200
Yes, Sir Tonyo.

361
00:15:46,333 --> 00:15:47,800
Besides, we can't decide

362
00:15:47,933 --> 00:15:49,967
