364
00:15:53,300 --> 00:15:54,467
Oh...

365
00:15:54,600 --> 00:15:57,567
Oh, I'm sorry.

366
00:15:57,700 --> 00:16:00,100
But I'm not an expert
on things like that.

367
00:16:00,233 --> 00:16:03,467
Geez, that's really humble,
Sir Tonyo.

368
00:16:05,900 --> 00:16:07,567
Do you like our outfit?

369
00:16:07,700 --> 00:16:09,533
Does it look ugly?

370
00:16:09,700 --> 00:16:11,633
Because I don't think
it's my type.

371
00:16:11,767 --> 00:16:15,033
Don't I look fat here,
Sir Tonyo?

372
00:16:16,067 --> 00:16:18,067
- This is okay, right?
- Yes.

373
00:16:19,267 --> 00:16:20,633
Oh...

374
00:16:21,700 --> 00:16:25,100
It seems like Sir Tonyo doesn't
like what we're wearing.

375
00:16:25,233 --> 00:16:26,400
-He just didn't want to say it.
-That's right.

376
00:16:26,533 --> 00:16:28,800
Don't worry, Sir Tonyo,
we'll change again.

377
00:16:28,933 --> 00:16:29,833
Let's go.

378
00:16:29,967 --> 00:16:32,900
Just sit down there,
Sir Tonyo, okay?

379
00:16:34,100 --> 00:16:35,933
Don't follow me into the room.

380
00:16:36,067 --> 00:16:38,233
In the room?

381
00:16:38,367 --> 00:16:40,233
Yeah, don't stand up, okay?

382
00:16:40,367 --> 00:16:41,233
Just stay there, okay?

383
00:16:41,400 --> 00:16:43,300
- Come on, Sis,.
- Come on.

384
00:16:48,300 --> 00:16:49,300
Oh...

385
00:16:49,433 --> 00:16:51,400
Please hurry up,
okay, because...

386
00:16:51,533 --> 00:16:53,000
I still have somewhere to go!

387
00:16:56,200 --> 00:16:58,167
Oh my God.

388
00:17:28,067 --> 00:17:29,767
Touching!

389
00:17:29,900 --> 00:17:30,967
A tear-jerker!

390
00:17:31,100 --> 00:17:32,667
- It's perfect!
- Really!

391
00:17:32,800 --> 00:17:33,800
You know, for sure,

392
00:17:33,933 --> 00:17:37,600
