- It's blank!

394
00:17:39,567 --> 00:17:41,067
Stop it!

395
00:17:41,200 --> 00:17:42,333
The more I can't even
think of anything.

396
00:17:42,467 --> 00:17:44,567
I can't type anything.

397
00:17:44,700 --> 00:17:46,933
Do you know why?

398
00:17:47,067 --> 00:17:51,700
Because resigning is not
entirely in your heart.

399
00:17:51,867 --> 00:17:52,833
You know, you're right.

400
00:17:52,967 --> 00:17:54,167
And for sure,

401
00:17:54,300 --> 00:17:56,400
