up being a police officer.

402
00:17:56,533 --> 00:17:58,067
- Right.
- Right, Bobby?

403
00:17:58,200 --> 00:17:59,633
Right.

404
00:17:59,767 --> 00:18:01,733
Of course, I'm thinking
about Grandma.

405
00:18:01,867 --> 00:18:03,733
We know that.

406
00:18:03,867 --> 00:18:06,467
But didn't Tonyo offer
a solution for you...

407
00:18:06,600 --> 00:18:08,233
to hire a caregiver...

408
00:18:08,367 --> 00:18:10,000
- for Captain?
- Yes, he did.

409
00:18:10,133 --> 00:18:12,600
Can you please
stop mentioning his name?

410
00:18:12,733 --> 00:18:14,300
Oh, statement!

411
00:18:14,433 --> 00:18:16,267
Attitude!

412
00:18:33,333 --> 00:18:35,700
This, Sir Tonyo, is it perfect?

413
00:18:35,833 --> 00:18:37,033
Yes, that's right.

414
00:18:37,167 --> 00:18:38,400
Apple and I are twinning, oh.

415
00:18:38,533 --> 00:18:40,100
Is this okay?

416
00:18:40,233 --> 00:18:42,067
Oh...

417
00:18:42,200 --> 00:18:43,767
No matter what you wear,

418
00:18:43,900 --> 00:18:45,300
it will still suit you.

419
00:18:47,033 --> 00:18:48,867
Really?

420
00:18:49,000 --> 00:18:49,800
Of course.

421
00:18:49,933 --> 00:18:51,133
I'm not going to lie.

422
00:18:51,267 --> 00:18:54,067
That's why we love you so much,
Sir Tonyo.

423
00:18:54,200 --> 00:18:55,400
Sorry,

424
00:18:55,567 --> 00:18:57,700
but I really have to go

425
00:18:57,833 --> 00:19:00,400
because I might not
catch Bobby at her house.

426
00:19:00,533 --> 00:19:02,400
Oh, that's right, Sir Tonyo.

427
00:19:02,533 --> 00:19:04,300
Sorry, we bothered you.

428
00:19:04,433 --> 00:19:05,867
That's right, Sir Tonyo.

429
00:19:06,000 --> 00:19:07,033
Good luck.

430
00:19:07,167 --> 00:19:09,167
We hope you and Ma'am Bobby
will patch things up.

431
00:19:09,300 --> 00:19:11,633
We're Team TonBy.

432
00:19:11,767 --> 00:19:13,133
Thank you.

433
00:19:13,267 --> 00:19:15,233
Well...

434
00:19:15,367 --> 00:19:16,367
I have to go.

435
00:19:16,500 --> 00:19:17,300
Wait!

436
00:19:17,433 --> 00:19:18,967
Let's take a selfie first,
Sir Tonyo.

437
00:19:19,100 --> 00:19:20,533
- Selfie?
- That's right, Sir Tonyo.

438
00:19:21,933 --> 00:19:22,767
Oh, wait, wait, wait.

439
00:19:22,900 --> 00:19:24,567
Can you put your arm around us,
Sir Tonyo.

440
00:19:24,700 --> 00:19:25,200
Okay.

441
00:19:26,733 --> 00:19:29,367
Smile!

442
00:19:29,533 --> 00:19:31,167
Perfect!

443
00:19:31,300 --> 00:19:33,300
Thank you very much, Sir Tonyo.

444
00:19:33,433 --> 00:19:34,167
I'm leaving now, okay?

445
00:19:34,300 --> 00:19:36,100
Okay, I'm really going to be
late.

446
00:19:36,233 --> 00:19:38,133
- Okay, okay, bye.
- Thank you, Sir Tonyo.

447
00:19:38,267 --> 00:19:39,233
Sorry again.

448
00:19:39,367 --> 00:19:39,933
Okay!

449
00:19:41,567 --> 00:19:43,433
Let's look at the picture.

450
00:19:43,567 --> 00:19:44,367
Hey...

451
00:19:44,500 --> 00:19:45,933
We're so cute there, Sis.

452
00:19:46,067 --> 00:19:47,367
That's right, Sis, post it?

453
00:19:47,500 --> 00:19:48,967
Okay, but let's choose.

454
00:19:49,100 --> 00:19:50,133
That one!

455
00:19:50,267 --> 00:19:53,067
You and Tonyo have been fighting
for a whle now, Bobby!

456
00:19:53,200 --> 00:19:55,600
That's right, aren't you going
to talk to Tonyo?

457
00:19:55,733 --> 00:19:57,833
Well, I'm resigning anyway,

458
00:19:57,967 --> 00:20:00,633
so we don't need
to talk anymore.

459
00:20:00,767 --> 00:20:01,667
- Oh!
- Oh!

460
00:20:01,800 --> 00:20:03,133
Well, consistent!

461
00:20:03,300 --> 00:20:04,400
With an attitude!

462
00:20:04,533 --> 00:20:06,567
But, girl, you know,
you know the saying...

463
00:20:06,700 --> 00:20:08,433
- The more you hate...
- The more you love.

464
00:20:08,567 --> 00:20:11,233
Hey, I don't love him.

465
00:20:11,367 --> 00:20:12,700
- Okay!
- Okay!

466
00:20:12,833 --> 00:20:14,800
- Okay, you said so...
- You said so...

467
00:20:14,933 --> 00:20:16,733
We said it at the same time.

468
00:20:16,867 --> 00:20:18,200
- That's true!
- Okay.

469
00:20:18,333 --> 00:20:20,433
I'll sit down,
I got tired, Friend.

470
00:20:20,567 --> 00:20:22,700
Oh! Friend, quick!

471
00:20:22,833 --> 00:20:24,600
Come here first, Abdul!

472
00:20:24,733 --> 00:20:26,233
Why are you pulling me?
What's that?

473
00:20:26,367 --> 00:20:29,500
Look at this post that Tonyo is
tagged in, see?

474
00:20:29,633 --> 00:20:30,633
Oh, winner!

475
00:20:30,767 --> 00:20:32,467
Girl, we can't blame Tonyo.

476
00:20:32,600 --> 00:20:33,533
That's right!

477
00:20:33,667 --> 00:20:35,100
Well, that's because Bobby
doesn't like him.

478
00:20:36,133 --> 00:20:36,967
What's that?

479
00:20:37,100 --> 00:20:39,733
Tonyo, holding
two women in his arms!

480
00:20:39,867 --> 00:20:42,700
And then the two women are
wearing two piece bikinis!

481
00:20:42,833 --> 00:20:44,500
I can almost see their chest!

482
00:20:44,633 --> 00:20:46,267
- Oh my!
- Right?

483
00:20:46,400 --> 00:20:49,233
And Sir Tonyo's gaze
seems so sticky here.

484
00:20:49,367 --> 00:20:51,267
- And he's so close!
- It means something!

485
00:20:51,400 --> 00:20:53,200
- Yes! Oh my, maybe...
- It seems like he likes it.

486
00:20:53,333 --> 00:20:56,233
Tonyo can feel the woman's body.

487
00:20:56,367 --> 00:20:57,400
- Oh, yes, right?
- Even though...

488
00:20:57,533 --> 00:20:59,533
- Oh, seriously, so close!
- Yes.

489
00:20:59,667 --> 00:21:01,567
- What's that? Let me see.
- Oh!

490
00:21:01,700 --> 00:21:04,333
- You don't want it, right?
- Bobby's being envious.

491
00:21:04,467 --> 00:21:06,567
- Then don't.
- Really!

492
00:21:06,700 --> 00:21:08,333
You don't want it, right?

493
00:21:08,500 --> 00:21:10,167
See it for yourself.

494
00:21:10,300 --> 00:21:11,333
She looked at it.

495
00:21:11,467 --> 00:21:13,233
Friend, she couldn't stand it
