496
00:21:13,367 --> 00:21:15,000
Arms around, right?

497
00:21:21,633 --> 00:21:22,533
Oh, where are you going?

498
00:21:22,667 --> 00:21:23,800
Does it hurt?

499
00:21:23,933 --> 00:21:24,733
Ouch.

500
00:21:24,867 --> 00:21:26,367
It hurts more when I hit you.

501
00:21:26,500 --> 00:21:28,200
Step aside.

502
00:21:28,633 --> 00:21:30,367
She's really mean.

503
00:21:30,500 --> 00:21:31,667
She's acting like that even
though she doesn't love him yet.

504
00:21:31,800 --> 00:21:32,700
Yes, right?

505
00:21:32,833 --> 00:21:33,767
She likes that!

506
00:21:33,900 --> 00:21:35,267
You like it, don't you?

507
00:21:35,400 --> 00:21:36,900
Tonyo's arms are around them,
like that, see?

508
00:21:37,400 --> 00:21:39,000
Hey, friend,
I want some barbecue.

509
00:21:39,133 --> 00:21:40,267
You know, you're always hungry.

510
00:21:40,400 --> 00:21:41,900
You're really hungry, right?

511
00:21:42,067 --> 00:21:43,033
- You don't seem to know me.
- Mar!

512
00:21:43,167 --> 00:21:44,067
- Abdul!
- Oh...

513
00:21:44,200 --> 00:21:45,667
Is Bobby at home?

514
00:21:45,800 --> 00:21:47,367
- Oh...
- Oh...

515
00:21:47,500 --> 00:21:50,800
She's gone. She left already.

516
00:21:50,933 --> 00:21:52,567
Where did Bobby go, by the way?

517
00:21:52,700 --> 00:21:55,433
You know, Tonyo,
we'd like to warn you.

518
00:21:55,567 --> 00:21:56,833
Well...

519
00:21:56,967 --> 00:22:00,133
Bobby saw your selfie

520
00:22:00,267 --> 00:22:04,100
