who are allergic to clothes!

521
00:22:04,233 --> 00:22:06,233
But that doesn't mean anything.

522
00:22:06,367 --> 00:22:07,833
No, no.

523
00:22:07,967 --> 00:22:10,633
But to an angry person,
everything has a meaning.

524
00:22:11,467 --> 00:22:12,433
- Am I right?
- Correct!

525
00:22:12,567 --> 00:22:13,667
Yes, you're right!

526
00:22:13,800 --> 00:22:15,367
Perfect!

527
00:22:27,367 --> 00:22:28,733
Good job!

528
00:22:28,867 --> 00:22:30,700
Oh, sorry, sorry, sorry.

529
00:22:32,567 --> 00:22:34,033
I didn't know you easily get
startled.

530
00:22:34,167 --> 00:22:36,067
I don't easily get startled.
I'm traumatized, remember?

531
00:22:36,200 --> 00:22:37,733
The last time I experienced
that, I was kidnapped,

532
00:22:37,867 --> 00:22:38,967
- taken to another country.
- Sorry, sorry.

533
00:22:39,100 --> 00:22:40,900
You were the one who saved me!

534
00:22:41,033 --> 00:22:42,133
Sorry, sorry.

535
00:22:42,267 --> 00:22:46,900
I saw you on your way out,
walking, so I followed you.

536
00:22:47,033 --> 00:22:48,733
What are you doing here?

537
00:22:48,900 --> 00:22:50,267
I brought your snack.

538
00:22:50,400 --> 00:22:53,467
I left it with Sir Torres.

539
00:22:53,600 --> 00:22:54,400
Oh...

540
00:22:54,533 --> 00:22:55,767
Okay, I'm leaving.

541
00:22:55,900 --> 00:22:58,900
Oh, Selena, Selena,
wait a minute.

542
00:22:59,033 --> 00:23:02,567
I'm sorry about earlier, okay?

543
00:23:02,700 --> 00:23:05,900
I used you to impress others.

544
00:23:06,033 --> 00:23:08,000
Oh, is that it?

545
00:23:08,133 --> 00:23:09,933
It's nothing, that's okay.

546
00:23:10,067 --> 00:23:14,800
Well, I wish you had told me so
I could have improved my acting.

547
00:23:14,933 --> 00:23:19,467
I never thought you'd play along
with my schemes.

548
00:23:22,467 --> 00:23:24,533
Selena...

549
00:23:24,667 --> 00:23:26,533
the...

550
00:23:26,667 --> 00:23:29,167
the one you said earlier...

551
00:23:29,300 --> 00:23:32,800
that there are a lot of things
you like about me.

552
00:23:32,933 --> 00:23:33,867
Are you serious about that?

553
00:23:34,000 --> 00:23:36,667
Or are you just fooling me?

554
00:23:36,800 --> 00:23:37,667
Of course.

555
00:23:37,800 --> 00:23:39,133
Why would I lie?

556
00:23:40,633 --> 00:23:42,867
Oh...

557
00:23:43,000 --> 00:23:45,067
What's that?
What's the "Oh..." for?

558
00:23:46,300 --> 00:23:48,933
Oh...
Oh...

559
00:23:49,067 --> 00:23:51,567
Do you want me
to bring you home?

560
00:23:51,700 --> 00:23:55,600
It's late at night,
it's dark, it's dangerous.

561
00:23:55,767 --> 00:23:57,600
Right?

562
00:23:57,733 --> 00:24:00,367
Okay.

563
00:24:00,500 --> 00:24:02,300
Let me just get my car, okay?

564
00:24:02,433 --> 00:24:03,967
I'll come back, okay?

565
00:24:06,133 --> 00:24:07,933
Boo!

566
00:24:08,067 --> 00:24:09,300
What's that? What are you doing?

567
00:24:09,433 --> 00:24:10,233
Nothing.

568
00:24:10,367 --> 00:24:12,100
I was supposed to bring someone
home,

569
00:24:12,233 --> 00:24:14,233
but when I turned around,
she was gone.

570
00:24:14,367 --> 00:24:15,400
Just over there by the Balete.

571
00:24:15,533 --> 00:24:16,133
Okay, okay!

572
00:24:17,600 --> 00:24:19,733
He looks like an idiot.

573
00:24:28,200 --> 00:24:29,400
What are you doing there?

574
00:24:29,567 --> 00:24:31,733
We went to Miss Donabel's house.

575
00:24:31,867 --> 00:24:33,167
We saw her.

576
00:24:33,300 --> 00:24:35,733
But Mar and Abdul were there.

577
00:24:35,867 --> 00:24:37,533
Does that mean they killed her?

578
00:24:37,667 --> 00:24:40,400
Our suspect is one
of Miss Calabari's staff?

579
00:24:40,533 --> 00:24:42,067
We need someone for the pageant.

580
00:24:42,200 --> 00:24:43,567
I can volunteer to audition.

581
00:24:43,700 --> 00:24:45,333
We need someone else to join.

582
00:24:45,467 --> 00:24:48,500
I'm also auditioning
for Miss Calabari.

583
00:24:51,067 --> 00:24:52,100
That's awesome, Bobby!

584
00:24:52,233 --> 00:24:53,267
You're a beauty pagent
contestant!

585
00:24:53,400 --> 00:24:55,267
Don't worry, Bobby.

586
00:24:55,400 --> 00:24:57,367
Mar and I will take care of you.

587
00:24:57,500 --> 00:24:58,767
Right?
